  "commit_message": "Fix sqlite race in LocalStore\n\nA write lock is needed for upgradeDBSchema. Otherwise, another process\ncan write to the database causing error `SQLITE_BUSY_SNAPSHOT` (517) to\nbe returned.\n\nThis also wraps upgradeDBSchema in a !readOnly guard, since it performs\ndatabase writes.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lisanna Dettwyler <lisanna.dettwyler@gmail.com>",
